<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-28-0107 </DOCNO><TEXT>The main topics of the scientific programme of this congress are the applicationof new radiopharmaceuticals in diagnosis and therapy, their pharmacokinetics,chemistry and radiation doses in patients, immunoscintigraphy, emissioncomputer tomography and nuclear magnetic resonance. New radioimmunoassaysand diagnostic studies in different medical fields such as oncology,endocrinology, nephrology, cardiology, gastroenterology, neurology, pulmonology,haematology and bone/joint diseases are presented as well as modern imagingcameras and scanners with digital or data processing systems, variouscollimators and crystals. Some papers deal with the quality control ofcamera and computer systems and artificial intelligence.</TEXT></DOC>